Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya, have you heard? Murota 9-dan, the head\Nof the pros committee, gave Shindou a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.22,0:01:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked if Shindou was sick or needed to file\Nfor leave, but he didn't get a clear answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:01:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.08,0:02:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's going to quit being a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.57,0:02:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And to think people thought he could become Touya's rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Genius is meaningless if you don't play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:18.27,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If I were to want to play...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:22.88,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If I were to play Go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:29.46,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai would be gone forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.55,0:02:31.52,Thinking,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:35.37,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I... I'm afraid of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:46.15,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs28}The Sixty-Ninth Match\N\N{\fs}The Determined Visitor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.23,0:03:03.68,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I haven't been in Japan for two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:14.54,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The pro exams are approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:18.61,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Kadowaki, the former holder of three\Nstudent titles. Will be taking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.48,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's finally starting next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.66,0:03:26.06,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I wonder how everyone's doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:29.43,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The results from the match last week...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.79,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Ochi beat Mashiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:35.70,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Waya didn't have a match...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:37.94,Thinking,,0,0,0,,And Shindou...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.27,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Forfeit!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:03:59.31,Background,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You would look like you had just come back from\Ntraining if you had a beard or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised when you called.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How was China?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Le Ping! You grew up so quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:23.97,Background,,0,0,0,,So that's what you were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.81,0:04:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's good that Le Ping started following me around and studying, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,he was always glaring at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What a brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just a kid, but he's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I did end up becoming good friends with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All thanks to the Waya medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave him some medicine when\Nhe got a stomach ache.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember? The kind you always\Ntake when you have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:05:01.16,Background,,0,0,0,,I figured since he looks just like you, the\Nmedicine would work on him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it worked like a charm,\Nand we became good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your match against that Zhao Shi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost... Zhao got Yang Hai-san's MD player.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won the next time we played!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:29.73,Background,,0,0,0,,We played a few times after that, too.\NAnd I renewed my visa over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:33.48,Background,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I played all that I could\Nduring the last two months,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,surrounded by the top players of China,\Nand the future top players of China.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won against a few people, and above\Nall I've gained confidence in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Yeah, what was it you wanted to ask\Nme about that you mentioned on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:56.76,Background,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:06:01.17,Background,,0,0,0,,I picked one up to read all this\Ntime, and Shindou had a forfeit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see him again before\Nthe pro exams, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the only match Shindou\Nhas a forfeit on, Isumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:25.00,Background,,0,0,0,,It's been like that since May.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't trip now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.17,Background,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:34.83,Background,,0,0,0,,It seems like he doesn't want to play Go anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:47.29,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Isumi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard from Mr. Narusawa, you were studying\Nin China? When did you get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind telling me what the young\Nplayers there were like sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll contact you later then, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:31.64,Background,,0,0,0,,U-Umm... Amono-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard anything about Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou Hikaru first dan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand why he hasn't gone\Nto any of the matches, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Ogata Jyudan asked\Nme about it earlier, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Ogata?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:02.66,Background,,0,0,0,,Master Ogata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You played Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, towards the end of Golden Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,One night during the Go seminar\Nrun by the Go institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To the best of my knowledge, he hasn't gone to\Nany matches or the Wakajishisen since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Was anything out of the ordinary\Nwhen he played you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the ordinary?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me know if you learn anything about Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:02.35,Background,,0,0,0,,So he hasn't come here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:09.20,Background,,0,0,0,,I'd beat him to a pulp if he did. Yelling,\N"What the hell are you thinking!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know exactly what, but Kawai-san\Nremember what you said about visiting Shuusaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuusaku? As in Honinbou Shuusaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was towards the end of Golden\NWeek. I bumped into him during work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did you know that I'm a taxi driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it looked like he was going on a trip\Nso I asked him where he was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He said Innoshima, so I went with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it was where Shuusaku was\Nborn, I was interested, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:57.54,Background,,0,0,0,,And the kid ran around everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:05.29,Background,,0,0,0,,The Shuusaku memorial at Ishikiri Shrine, Housenji\NTemple, Itosaki Hachibanguu, Jikanji Temple...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:08.30,Background,,0,0,0,,Even to Honmyouji Temple in Sugamo\Nwhen we got back to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.92,Background,,0,0,0,,Man, I was busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And how was Shindou during the trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he act out of the ordinary?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... now that I think about\Nit, he seemed really panicky...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As if he was in a hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed like he was searching for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Searching for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:16.21,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.02,0:11:26.97,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you playing, Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.84,Ed5English,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\c&H000000&\shad0\bord0\b1\pos(203,295)}Shindou{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.11,0:11:34.23,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make you tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:44.23,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for coming without calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be home from school soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I'll bring you some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.95,0:12:13.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of dust on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:18.34,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He really hasn't been playing... Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... Isumi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, why were you in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.49,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It wasn't Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:52.96,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I felt that someone was in my\Nroom, so I was hopeful, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:57.03,Thinking,,0,0,0,,it wasn't... Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He just got here. I'll bring you some tea, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been awhile, Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san, you were in China?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was studying there the last two months,\Nand I just got back a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:32.50,Background,,0,0,0,,But more imporantly, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:36.75,Background,,0,0,0,,Waya told me you haven't been going to\Nany of the matches or study sessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:43.41,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Oh man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.56,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Should I run away somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:52.10,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But I can't leave Isumi-san here,\NI haven't seen him in so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that Touya was your rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:14:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you lose your will to play because you thought\Nyou would never catch up to Touya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.41,0:14:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, I don't stand a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't know? He's playing\Nat an incredible level already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,An incredible level?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Players rising in rank... Touya...\Nhe's 3-dan already!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And look at the section above that about\Nthis week's matches, under today's date.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:32.68,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Hagiwara 9-dan, Touya 3-dan... Honinbou\Nmatch, third preliminaries, final match.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Final match of the third preliminaries!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kuwabara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your match is already over, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. My opponent, Mano, is taking his\Ntime thinking, so I came for a smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Touya's successor doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fighting everywhere. It's\Na difficult game for both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But it would be incredible if Touya-kun were to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:31.58,Background,,0,0,0,,Third dan at the age of fifteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who's been a pro for two years\Nentering the Honinbou league...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurata-kun lost to you, Master,\Nin this year's Honinbou match.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But when Touya-kun joins in for the competition to\Nbecome the Honinbou challenger for next year,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the new wave will finally be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:57.49,Background,,0,0,0,,But I wonder what's wrong with Shindou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:16:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To think he had the attention of Master Kuwabara,\NMaster Ogata, and even Master Touya Kouyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:09.70,Background,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, hardship and\Ndoubt are both necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:14.37,Background,,0,0,0,,Amono-san, I'm not worried at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as that successor of Touya's, who dragged\Nthat brat into the world of the pros,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is struggling hard to reach the top, there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:30.15,Background,,0,0,0,,He will return...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:35.17,Background,,0,0,0,,before the opponent that he needs to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You speak as if Shindou-kun is\NTouya-Kun's destined rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're overestimating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not overestimating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya Akira himself thinks so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:12.07,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Touya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:15.44,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's already gotten this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If he wins today,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll join a league of eight top pros to compete\Nfor the right to challenge Master Kuwabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How strong has he gotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like you still love the game,\Nwhy don't you play it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'm... not interested in this stuff. Besides, what\Nbusiness of it is yours if I quit playing Go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit playing Go!? Are you serious!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:32.51,Background,,0,0,0,,Wait, Isumi-san! I don't want\Nto play! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying this out of concern for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Play me... play me for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I...sumi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou, do you remember? The match between\Nus during the pro exams last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:06.00,Memory,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I went to Atari from the wrong side!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.77,0:19:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I... that match last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When I resigned for violating the Hagashi rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,During that long period when I considered my violation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When I thought about whether I could\Npretend that I didn't violate the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bitter memory for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the last match I played against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:20:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to play a clean game against\Nyou before the pro exams this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me start again from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:25.41,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:29.96,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If I play Go again... Sai won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:12.64,Op3Kanji,,0,0,0,,胸の鼓動　熱くゆるがす
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:16.55,Op3Kanji,,0,0,0,,刺激求めて歩く My Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.55,0:00:20.71,Op3Kanji,,0,0,0,,時間だけが過ぎる毎日じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:22.71,Op3Kanji,,0,0,0,,変化はない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:27.97,Op3Kanji,,0,0,0,,止まらない　信じたい　進みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:31.98,Op3Kanji,,0,0,0,,自分の力試す My Life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.11,0:00:36.19,Op3Kanji,,0,0,0,,でも早歩きしたって見落とすだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:38.22,Op3Kanji,,0,0,0,,そう確実に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:45.98,Op3Kanji,,0,0,0,,明日は明日の風が吹く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:55.30,Op3Kanji,,0,0,0,,それでも　今この瞬間を強く生きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:01.31,Op3Kanji,,0,0,0,,さまよったとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:05.25,Op3Kanji,,0,0,0,,見たことない世界でも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:11.02,Op3Kanji,,0,0,0,,何よりも 自分を信じ立ち向かおう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:16.87,Op3Kanji,,0,0,0,,どんな場所にいても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.03,0:01:20.75,Op3Kanji,,0,0,0,,つつむ空は一つだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:25.61,Op3Kanji,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　もっと 翼広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.22,0:01:29.30,Op3Kanji,,0,0,0,,羽ばたけるよね
